data.description: Kimberling City Patio Home! Enjoy the perfect lake getaway only seconds away from Table Rock Lake and Downtown Kimberling City! This cozy 3 bedroom 3 bath lake close retreat offers all your needs without breaking your wallet. Inside fall in love with a spacious, open concept floor plan on main level with cozy wood burning fireplace in living ready to warm your heart this holiday season. Speaking of the holidays, enjoy ample room for entertaining and meal prep in spacious kitchen/dining area with loads of cabinet space, stainless steel appliances, and walk out to covered back deck offering peaceful wooded views, cool lake breezes, endless star gazing, and the soul soothing sounds of nature. Back inside main level offers cozy guest bedroom, full guest bath, and massive owners ensuite boasting mini spa retreat with walk-in shower, jetted corner tub ready to soak the day away, and personal favorite, private second sitting room with loads of natural light through oversized double windows (also make great home office or nursery). Need even more room for football season?! Lower level offers second living/entertaining space with third bedroom and full bath along with walk out to outdoor patio in level/gently sloping park like setting. Bonus! Attached one car carport offers plenty of storage options for boat, lake toys and your lake lifestyle. Convenient Kimberling City water & sewer also available and again the Location just minutes to heart of Kimberling City with local boutiques & eateries, spas, seasonal farmers market, grocery store, post office & all your lake needs at popular Port of Kimberling Marina including floating restaurant, ski shop, fishing gear, slip & boat rentals and more. Local tip! Take a UTV/golf cart anywhere within city limits (with the proper safety equipment and speed limit restrictions). New memories and new adventures begin here at 38 James River Rd in heart of lake loving Kimberling City.
